 563:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   These parameters have an impact on ADC scope: ADC group injected.
 564:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to corresponding unitary functions into
 565:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @ref ADC_LL_EF_Configuration_ADC_Group_Regular
 566:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (functions with prefix "INJ").
 567:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   The setting of these parameters by function @ref LL_ADC_INJ_Init()
 568:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         is conditioned to ADC state:
 569:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC instance must be disabled.
 570:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This condition is applied to all ADC features, for efficiency
 571:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and compatibility over all STM32 series. However, the different
 572:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         features can be set under different ADC state conditions
 573:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (setting possible with ADC enabled without conversion on going,
 574:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC enabled with conversion on going, ...)
 575:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Each feature can be updated afterwards with a unitary function
 576:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and potentially with ADC in a different state than disabled,
 577:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         refer to description of each function for setting
 578:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         conditioned to ADC state.
 579:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   */
