4836:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           are defined by channel number.
4837:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           This function retrieves:
