4840:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             rank of each channel is fixed by channel HW number.
4841:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             (channel 0 fixed on rank 0, channel 1 fixed on rank1, ...).
4842:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Sequence direction: Unless specified in parameters, sequencer
4843:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             scan direction is forward (from lowest channel number to
4844:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             highest channel number).
4845:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Sequencer ranks are selected using
