5063:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           process the returned value with the helper macro
5064:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           @ref __LL_ADC_CHANNEL_TO_DECIMAL_NB().
