5819:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
5820:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC group injected contexts queue mode.
5821:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   A context is a setting of group injected sequencer:
5822:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - group injected trigger
5823:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - sequencer length
5824:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - sequencer ranks
5825:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         If contexts queue is disabled:
5826:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - only 1 sequence can be configured
5827:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           and is active perpetually.
5828:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         If contexts queue is enabled:
5829:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - up to 2 contexts can be queued
5830:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           and are checked in and out as a FIFO stack (first-in, first-out).
5831:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - If a new context is set when queues is full, error is triggered
5832:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           by interruption "Injected Queue Overflow".
5833:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Two behaviors are possible when all contexts have been processed:
5834:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           the contexts queue can maintain the last context active perpetually
5835:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           or can be empty and injected group triggers are disabled.
5836:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Triggers can be only external (not internal SW start)
5837:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Caution: The sequence must be fully configured in one time
ARM GAS  C:\Users\alexc\AppData\Local\Temp\cccRnhkW.s 			page 122


5838:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           (one write of register JSQR makes a check-in of a new context
5839:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           into the queue).
5840:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Therefore functions to set separately injected trigger and
5841:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           sequencer channels cannot be used, register JSQR must be set
5842:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           using function @ref LL_ADC_INJ_ConfigQueueContext().
5843:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   This parameter can be modified only when no conversion is on going
5844:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on either groups regular or injected.
5845:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   A modification of the context mode (bit JQDIS) causes the contexts
5846:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         queue to be flushed and the register JSQR is cleared.
5847:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
5848:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
5849:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be disabled or enabled without conversion on going
5850:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on either groups regular or injected.
5851:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CFGR     JQM            LL_ADC_INJ_SetQueueMode\n
5852:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         CFGR     JQDIS          LL_ADC_INJ_SetQueueMode
5853:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
5854:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  QueueMode This parameter can be one of the following values:
