6992:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - groups monitored: not selection possible (monitoring on both
6993:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             groups regular and injected).
6994:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             Channels selected are monitored on groups regular and injected:
6995:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNELxx_REG_INJ (do not use parameters
6996:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNELxx_REG and LL_ADC_AWD_CHANNELxx_INJ)
