6998:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             12 bits the 4 LSB are ignored, if ADC resolution is 10 bits
6999:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             the 2 LSB are ignored.
7000:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   If ADC oversampling is enabled, ADC analog watchdog thresholds are
7001:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         impacted: the comparison of analog watchdog thresholds is done on
