7003:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC data register bitfield [15:4] (12 most significant bits).
7004:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Examples:
7005:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Oversampling ratio and shift selected to have ADC conversion data
7006:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           on 12 bits (ratio 16 and shift 4, or ratio 32 and shift 5, ...):
7007:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           ADC analog watchdog thresholds must be divided by 16.
7008:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Oversampling ratio and shift selected to have ADC conversion data
7009:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           on 14 bits (ratio 16 and shift 2, or ratio 32 and shift 3, ...):
7010:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           ADC analog watchdog thresholds must be divided by 4.
7011:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Oversampling ratio and shift selected to have ADC conversion data
7012:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           on 16 bits (ratio 16 and shift none, or ratio 32 and shift 1, ...):
7013:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           ADC analog watchdog thresholds match directly to ADC data register.
