7597:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In case of ADC calibration necessary: When ADC is in deep-power-down
7598:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         state, the internal analog calibration is lost. After exiting from
7599:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         deep power down, calibration must be relaunched or calibration factor
7600:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (preliminarily saved) must be set back into calibration register.
7601:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
7602:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
7603:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be ADC disabled.
7604:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CR       DEEPPWD        LL_ADC_DisableDeepPowerDown
